lead_paragraph: The United States won the men's 4x100 meters medley relay on Saturday after Ryan Murphy had given them a world record start that propelled Michael Phelps to a 23rd gold medal in his final Olympic race.

headline.main: Swimming: U.S. Wins Men's Medley Relay, Golden Send-Off for Phelps
